Plain text file for dev (me) documentation

Combat system

Player:
    stamina & mana
    normal attack -> stamina
    magic attack -> stamina & mana
    turn ends when stamina == 0 or stamina > attack or spell with less stamina
    can end turn with command
    every choice is command not number

Print attack list

    command -> stats show attacks/spells
               ^     ^    ^
               |     |    stat to show
               |     command action
               command
    
    #--#--#--#--#--# Attacks (or Spells) #--#--#--#--#--#
    #                                                   #
        Attack_name    Stamina:number    Mana:Number
        Attack_name    Stamina:number    Mana:Number
        Attack_name    Stamina:number    Mana:Number
        Attack_name    Stamina:number    Mana:Number
        Attack_name    Stamina:number    Mana:Number
        max 20 per page
    #                                                   #
    #--#--#--#--#--#        Pag 1        #--#--#--#--#--#